{"tid":2116854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滴滴出行擬本港上市目標估值逾6千億港元     螞蟻擬香港上海同步上市目標估值逾2千億美元","createTime":"2020-07-20T12:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T12:57:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c2369f9d9063048a20cdcd815b2e0cbb025f5ee6","tid":2116854,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:11:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538897-20200720.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538897-20200720.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=f708fc96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538897-20200720.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bebb8470\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538897-20200720.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒引述消息人士報道，滴滴出行正與投資銀行洽談，計劃最快今年內在香港上市，目標估值逾6000億港元，即大約800億美元，有望成為近年香港市場規模最大新股交易之一。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，滴滴旗下包括網約車、單車，代駕以及金融業務已經規模化盈利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538905-20200720.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538905-20200720.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=b30bf990\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538905-20200720.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9fd6df05\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538905-20200720.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴旗下、支付寶母公司螞蟻集團宣布，啟動在上海科創板及港交所尋求同步上市計劃。<br />\n<br />\n螞蟻集團董事長井賢棟表示，上市可以讓集團更透明地面對世界、公眾，更好地與全社會分享成果和未來，又指欣喜地看到科創板和聯交所推出一系列改革和創新措施，為新經濟公司能更好地獲得資本市場支持，包括國際資本支持創造良好條件。<br />\n<br />\n路透社較早時引述兩名消息人士報道，螞蟻正計劃香港上市，最快今年實現，目標估值超過2000億美元。<br />\n<br />\n根據阿里巴巴年報，阿里持有螞蟻金服33%股權，阿里前主席馬雲持股8.8%，但對螞蟻擁有50%以上表決權。"},{"pid":"d5646c4a7e8072717aea9e2f2539094fe44a2f91","tid":2116854,"uid":1891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:12:23.000Z","msg":"借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jDOzNv1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjDOzNv1.jpg&h=62b7e60e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗片backup<br />\n何君堯見鄉黑(7 21)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/utmdfj8l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Futmdfj8l&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=0a5bc2d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/utmdfj8l</a><br />\n立場姐姐被元朗白衣人圍毆片段，亦有記者被打至爆鼻。現場並無任何警察。(7 21)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/mzd53a21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fmzd53a21&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=494be2c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/mzd53a21</a><br />\n黑社會元朗西鐵站打人片段(721)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/jxy71o5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fjxy71o5w&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=e5b7ca19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/jxy71o5w</a><br />\n黑社會元朗西鐵站車箱內打人片段(721)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/sbpzukcy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fsbpzukcy&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=ed1d36ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/sbpzukcy</a><br />\n【黑社會元朗西鐵站打人片段】有被打市民跪地 有被打市民跪地求唔好再傷害大家 最後被一拳打落地(721)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/uhkw5g0p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fuhkw5g0p&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=1bce594c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/uhkw5g0p</a><br />\n（元朗）有大肚婆被打到訓低左(721)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/phqyvf2h\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.c